Title: An Act Changing the Name of Pangpang Bridge Along the Antique-Aklan Road in the Province of Antique to Marcos Yee-Jonathan Gallo Memorial Bridge
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 887
An Act Changing the Name of Pangpang Bridge Along the Antique-Aklan Road in the Province of Antique to Marcos Yee-Jonathan Gallo Memorial Bridge
Section 1. The name of Pangpang Bridge along the Antique-Aklan Road in the Province of Antique is hereby changed to Marcos Yee-Jonathan Gallo Memorial Bridge.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. The Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: December 3, 1985
